    • numberOfSameValues

      public static java.lang.String numberOfSameValues​(int numberOfSameValues, int desiredNumOfSameValues, int amountOfTime)
      Method return a string with the number of same values and time it took to get them. eg. "Got 2 right! Took 7 years"
      Parameters:
      numberOfSameValues - number of same values
      desiredNumOfSameValues - desired number of same values, in this case 7 lotto numbers
      amountOfTime - indicates the amount of time it took
      Returns:
      returns a string with the parameter values within it

    • askAQuestion

      public static boolean askAQuestion​(java.lang.String question)
      Method is for asking user a question. "Y/N" will be added to the end of the question.
      Parameters:
      question - the question is asked from the user
      Returns:
      true or false, depending on the user input "Y/N" yes or no.
